OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy and
OL,6,Fdamp across England and Wales, with
OL,7,Foutbreaks of patchy rain. Clearer
OL,8,Fskies for much of Northern Ireland and
OL,9,FScotland. Though turning breezy with
OL,10,Fsome rain arriving across the far west
OL,11,Fof Northern Ireland and the Western
OL,12,FIsles.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FCloudy for many, with some
OL,15,Frain at times. The best of any sunnier
OL,16,Fbreaks most likely across southern and
OL,17,Feastern Scotland and later on across
OL,18,Fparts of southeast England.
